THE NORTH CAROLINA STATE BAR
v.
Willie D. GILBERT, II. No. 194P08. Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 11, 2008. Eric Michaux, Durham, for Gilbert. A. Root Edmonson, for State Bar. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 663 S.E.2d 1 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 23rd day of April 2008 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th day of December 2008."
